@startuml s-sokolko_smev3_adapter_service

actor Client
participant "API Layer\n(views.py)" as API
participant "QueryProcessor\n(processors/query.py)" as QueryProcessor
participant "Adapter\n(adapter.py)" as Adapter
participant "Model\n(models.py)" as Model
database MongoDB
participant "SMEV3 Adapter" as SMEV3

Client -> API: HTTP Request
activate API

API -> QueryProcessor: Process Query
activate QueryProcessor

QueryProcessor -> Adapter: Send SMEV3 Request
activate Adapter

Adapter -> SMEV3: SOAP Request
SMEV3 --> Adapter: SOAP Response

Adapter --> QueryProcessor: Response Data
deactivate Adapter

QueryProcessor -> Model: Save Query Data
activate Model

Model -> MongoDB: Store Data
MongoDB --> Model: Confirmation
Model --> QueryProcessor: Data Saved
deactivate Model

QueryProcessor --> API: Query Processed
deactivate QueryProcessor

API --> Client: HTTP Response
deactivate API

@enduml